23 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code Title 20, Chapter 77, Subchapter 1, is
24 amended to add an additional section to read as follows:
25 20-77-154. Reimbursement rate for mental health services and services
26 related to addiction.
27 (a) The Arkansas Medicaid Program shall:
28 (1) Set the reimbursement rate for mental health services and
29 services related to addiction to at least one hundred percent (100%) of the
30 Medicare reimbursement rate for the comparable service; and
31 (2) Reimburse for any mental health service or service related
32 to addiction that is offered or provided in the surrounding states.
33 (b) The Department of Human Services shall apply for any federal
34 waiver, Medicaid state plan amendment, or other authorization necessary to
35 implement this section.
